{"tid":863504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網民：萬聖節提早咗咩？「千年一遇美女」橋本環奈發福走晒樣","createTime":"2018-10-15T15:46:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T03:58:00.000Z","uid":147522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24fd2c7865e751642def9c093f2bec64eff8a800","tid":863504,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/15/234631_922fa4e4a5da4927fd4f2e3c5460d894.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F15%2F234631_922fa4e4a5da4927fd4f2e3c5460d894.png&h=d0f6bd6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年日本女星橋本環奈因為一張奇蹟美照爆紅，被網民封為「千年一見美少女」。外型甜美的她一向是宅男女神，但近日上節目卻被捕捉到疑似「走樣」，肥厚的雙下巴嚇倒不少人，更被指與渡邊直美撞樣。<br />\n<br />\n日前她為宣傳電視劇《我是大哥大》參加節目錄製，點知有網友發現她疑似發福，大笑時擠出雙下巴的截圖在網上瘋傳，不少人看了後都嚇到，說她「大走樣」，更有人說她看起來跟同場的諧星渡邊直美撞臉！"},{"pid":"f7170aa79d1634f8bfda919b0139353531b9f3d6","tid":863504,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"becky<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977ac8daaea7ed766bb2c5f0adfd62f4f9da77c3","tid":863504,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"樣靚肥瘦都係靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f8710a8518c63f5009ce4149c5229b6d73d667","tid":863504,"uid":129521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"食避孕藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f02c8f01ac8c879efc822ea317b6b613fdeb258","tid":863504,"uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T17:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Wm76zS-K6Pk/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FWm76zS-K6Pk%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=8ed513a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fbfddfb47efa252ccf4990773545247fa2871